  <brief_title>Comparison of INVOS and FORE SIGHT Cerebral Oximeter</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessing Cerebral Oxygenation During Different Surgical Procedures - Comparison of INVOS and ForeSight Cerebral Oximeter</official_title>
  <sponsors>
